{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.introN\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">introN</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">num</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hygienic</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult\">IntrosResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Introduces exactly `num` binders from the goal's target type.\n\nReturns `.goal newDecls mvarId` if successful where `newDecls` are the introduced free variable IDs,\n`mvarId` the updated goal.\nReturns `.failed` if it was not possible to introduce `num` new local declarations.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.introN","kind":"def","line":129,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.introN","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.lean#L129-L140"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.intros\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">intros</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">names</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">#[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.toArray\">]</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hygienic</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult\">IntrosResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Introduces leading binders (universal quantifiers and let-expressions) from the goal's target type.\n\nIf `names` is non-empty, introduces (at most) `names.size` binders using the provided names.\nIf `names` is empty, introduces all leading binders using names derived from the binder names;\n`hygienic` then controls whether those names are inaccessible (see `introCore`).\n\nReturns `.goal newDecls mvarId` with new introduced free variable Ids and the updated goal.\nReturns `.failed` if no new declaration was introduced.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.intros","kind":"def","line":110,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.intros","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.lean#L110-L127"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult.goal\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">IntrosResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">goal</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">newDecls</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.FVarId\">FVarId</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult\">IntrosResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult.goal","kind":"ctor","line":108,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult.goal","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.lean#L108-L108"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult.failed\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">IntrosResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">failed</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult\">IntrosResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult.failed","kind":"ctor","line":107,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult.failed","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.lean#L107-L107"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">IntrosResult</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult","kind":"inductive","line":106,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.IntrosResult","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Intro.lean#L106-L108"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaShareBuilder","Lean.Meta.Sym.InstantiateS","Lean.Meta.Sym.IsClass","Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Intro"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Intro"}